{
  "chapter": 36,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十六回「药王爷」。林琼菊醒来发现芮玮头痛剧烈，活死人以内家真元之气为芮玮驱毒疗伤，将黑毒逼至手掌。疗伤期间，一灯神尼趁机潜入墓中盗走活死人妻子的遗骨，活死人悲愤追出。芮玮醒后与林琼菊离开点苍山，发现红袍公和蓝髯客已被一灯神尼杀害——红袍公因传授飞龙八步、蓝髯客因传授化神掌而遭殃。二人立誓报仇后下山寻医，林琼菊以生意为名遍访药王爷的五处分号，半年间辗转大竹、湘潭、巨野皆未找到。芮玮毒势日重，二人最终来到南陵分号，遇一矮小猥琐的老头，此人正是隐于市的圣手如来药王爷，一眼看出芮玮中毒已深。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "菊妹，你醒了吗？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥，大哥！\n怎么啦？",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我……头……好……痛……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_huo_si_ren",
      "text": "前辈，我大哥不要紧吗？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_huo_si_ren",
      "text": "前辈……前辈……在用功时，那……那人进来的……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_si_ren",
      "speaker_name": "活死人",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "那人是谁？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_huo_si_ren",
      "text": "我……我……不知道……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_si_ren",
      "speaker_name": "活死人",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "你是死人吗，为什么不知道，快说是谁将我娘子盗去？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_si_ren",
      "speaker_name": "活死人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张玉珍，张玉珍，我知道是你，我知道是你……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "菊妹，你哭什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大……大哥……你……你的毒伤……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "菊妹，你别担心，我的伤不要紧。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我不信，我不信，这么厉害的毒伤会不要紧？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "这毒虽厉害，天下只有一人能救我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "是活死人吗？他……他……走了……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "大师伯去哪里了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "他是你大师伯？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那盗取尸骨的一定是一灯神尼！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "别哭，别哭……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大师伯走了，天下还有谁能救大哥……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "大师伯并不能治我毒伤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "那能救大哥的人是谁？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "你不认识，那人名叫圣手如来药王爷。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "咱们这就去找他吧。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老前辈，老前辈……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "红伯伯，红伯伯……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "他死了，是一灯杀死的。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "为什么？她为什么杀死红伯伯？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因……因为红伯伯传了我一套飞龙八步。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有他！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一灯贼尼！他哪里跟你作对啦？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道仅为了前辈传我一套化神掌？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论如何我要替前辈报仇。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "咱们先去开阳。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "开阳作什？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "去找药王爷啊！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "找药王爷？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "药王爷隐居的另外四个居处，都是极知名的闹市。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大隐于市，我以为药王爷在深山大泽隐居，真是大错而特错。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_xiao_huo_ji",
      "text": "找你们大掌柜的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "我就是大掌柜。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "那你一定是老板啦？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "可以这么说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "是就是，不是就不是，哪有可以这么说的道理。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "客官找老板有何贵干？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "我们是京里来的，有笔大生意找你们老板谈。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "多大生意，找我谈一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "你能做得主吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "千把两的黄金没有问题。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "可是一万两的生意？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "十万两。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "真有这么大的生意？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "你不信吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "我虽是这店的老板，但这票生意我不能做主，需找咱们的大老板谈谈。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "还有大老板？可是老板上的老板？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "咱们这小小药铺共有五号，每号有个老板，大老板则总管五处，大的生意就要找他说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "果然是老板上的老板，喂！大老板在不在这里啊？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "不在！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "你到大竹、湘潭、南陵、巨野四个地方的小小药铺去看看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "难道你说不准大老板到底在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "大老板五处地方各处走走，谁也无法断定他高兴到哪里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥，咱们去大竹。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥，这次一定能找着了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "菊妹，多亏你……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_xiao_huo_ji",
      "text": "大老板在吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_xiao_huo_ji",
      "text": "大老板在吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_suo_xiao_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "猥琐小老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "你们要买药吗？喂，小老鼠招呼招呼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "小伙计",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "要抓什么药？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_xiao_huo_ji",
      "text": "咱们要买最好的何首乌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "小伙计",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "买最好的何首乌，我可不敢做主。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "大掌柜",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "最好的何首乌，我们这里没有存货。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_da_zhang_gui",
      "text": "那怎么成，就要买来做药的啊！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "大掌柜",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "这里虽没有，就能拿来，姑娘要买几钱？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_da_zhang_gui",
      "text": "五斤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "大掌柜",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "姑娘说笑了，做药的哪要得了五斤。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_da_zhang_gui",
      "text": "我大哥病重非要五斤不可。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "大掌柜",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "一下哪收得到五斤最好的何首乌？",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_da_zhang_gui",
      "text": "小小药铺名重四方，哪会收不到五斤何首乌，找你们大老板来。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 393
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_suo_xiao_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "猥琐小老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "坐在那马上的可是姑娘的大哥？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_wei_suo_xiao_lao_tou",
      "text": "你们的大老板在不在？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "大掌柜",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "在，在。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_suo_xiao_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "猥琐小老头",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "就是十斤最好的何首乌也治不好你大哥！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    }
